# Passive Strategy
#
# This represents an extremely nieve strategy for playing the game. Basically,
# anything over 17, you stand. Anything less, you hit. Pretty simple. Great for
# testing.
#
# Difference in this and regular 'no_bust' is SOFT hands strategy.
# 'soft' hands strategy pulled from wizard_simple
###
